[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]Dr McGettigan: [bold]T
[normal]his is the decision you are making.  If you are running a company, you can obviously make these kinds of decisions.  You think, “Okay, I am getting £2
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]billion up front, effectively let us say £3
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]billion up front, but I am going to lose £3.25
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]billion.  That is my cash outflow over the run—£3.25
[normal]&#xa0;
