[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]Bahram Bekhradnia[bold]: The answer to the first is yes, up to a point, but do not forget it is a very important element of Government policy to increase the numbers in private and FE colleges just to increase the diversity of what is provided, so I do not think we should underestimate that.  What is really of concern and of some interest as well is 
[normal]that 
